              .small.text-muted.mb-2
                i.bi.bi-calendar3.me-1
                | March 2026
                span.ms-2
                  i.bi.bi-tag.me-1
                  | Free Resources
              h5.card-title
                a.text-decoration-none.text-dark(href="/blog/free-addiction-help-spokane.html")
                  | Free Addiction Help in Spokane, WA – 15 Resources You Didn't Know Existed
              p.card-text.text-muted Discover 15 free addiction recovery resources in Spokane most people never hear about — from peer support to emergency housing.
              a.btn.btn-outline-success.mt-auto(href="/blog/free-addiction-help-spokane.html")
                | Read More
                i.bi.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

